<[ Ak47_Dust_Final ]>

<[ Author : Robtronic ]>

This map is v2 of my ak47 dust arena map.

<[ Fixes ]>

1. Removed annoying console spam.

2.Added more props.

3.Added decals.

4.Added four secret area's.

5.Added three new guns.

6.Added a bomb site.

7.Added new surroundings such as buildings and new skybox.

8.Added more sounds and realistic distance blur fog.

Ok that about covers everything so i hope you enjoy the new version with the added bonus of the fps staying the same as the first version :)

<[ Enjoy ]>
